prompts.frontCover: A charming watercolor illustration of a slightly frazzled, but very happy, cartoon sloth hanging upside down from a party banner. The sloth is wearing a tiny, lopsided birthday party hat and holding a half-eaten slice of cake in one paw. Colorful, soft-hued confetti is gently drifting down around it. In the center, written in a beautiful, flowing, and readable handwritten cursive script, is the text "happy birthday... take it slow". The background is a clean, off-white with visible paper texture, featuring soft, organic watercolor bleeds of pastel pinks, blues, and yellows around the edges, enhancing the lighthearted and artistic feel. The entire design is a flat 2D artwork, capturing the essence of a hand-painted watercolor piece.
